  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807910/extras/9f05c2cd8245e8619b1b7d9f50cfd377.avif?t=1643381110\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br>Road Legends is a neon retro-futuristic racing game where you will race to music and collect bonuses on a rhythm basis<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807910/extras/ab632d584f1932b183c270a461b052cd.avif?t=1643381110\" width=600 height=294 /></span><br>You're on the road, although this time it's not a race where you need to be faster than your rivals! Just relax and drive through futuristic city!<br>Road Legends offers 10 challenging levels where you will put on test your reaction by collecting bonuses and avoiding obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807910/extras/72c3ec89d107f3df137835980a9ff59e.avif?t=1643381110\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br>Each level of the game comes with a unique soundtrack, which is perfectly synchronized with roadblocks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quick Feature List</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10 levels, each comes with a unique soundtrack<br></li><li> 3 different cars<br></li><li> Super addictive gameplay</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807910/extras/5d2bd116e402ab60164e08c740b87aa4.webp?t=1643381110\" width=600 height=50 /></span>",
